  <description><![CDATA[<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/maggiore-and-como-medley">Highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/maggiore-and-como-medley">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/maggiore-and-como-medley">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/maggiore-and-como-medley">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/maggiore-and-como-medley">Departure dates</a></h2>
</div>
<h3><a name="Hghlights"></a></h3>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Highlights</h3>
<ul>
<li>Experience the natural beauty of the Italian lakes</li>
<li>Spend time exploring the beautiful towns on Lake Como</li>
<li>Discover the elegant lakeside town of Stresa</li>
<li>Add on one of our fantastic excursions, to get even more out of your holiday (optional extras)</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/maggiore-and-como-medley">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h3><a name="Itinerary"></a></h3>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Example Itinerary</h3>
<p><strong>Day 1: UK to Lake Como</strong></p>
<p>Transfer by coach from the airport to <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a> to begin your stay in one of our hotels.</p>
<p><strong>Days 2-3: Lake Como</strong></p>
<p>Spend a few days soaking up the dramatic scenery on Lake Como. We recommend visiting the famous Villa Carlotta. Como Town is easy to get to, too. Take the local bus or ferry and enjoy the café culture of the provincial capital. The small town of Varenna is another beautiful place to check out with some great lake front restaurants where you can have a nice leisurely lunch. </p>
<p><strong>Day 4: St. Moritz &amp; the Bernina Express</strong></p>
<p>If you wanted a fun day out, head to Switzerland for a memorable day by booking onto our St. Moritz &amp; the Bernina train excursion (optional extra). This is our most popular excursion on Lake Como and this full-day outing includes time in Tirano where you can visit the remarkable cathedral. You'll also stop off in the quaint town of Chiavenna - the perfect place for grabbing for an ice-cream or coffee in the cobbled piazza. </p>
<p><strong>Day 5: Lake Como to Lake Maggiore</strong></p>
<p>Take a private transfer to <a data-udi="umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b}" title="Stresa">Stresa</a> on <a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="/{localLink:umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48}" title="Lake Maggiore">Lake Maggiore</a> where you'll spend the next seven nights at your chosen hotel.</p>
<p><strong>Days 7-10: Lake Maggiore</strong></p>
<p>Get to know Lake Maggiore. Based in Stresa<a data-udi="umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b}" title="Stresa">,</a> you’ll be at the centre of it all. We recommend visiting the Borromean Islands, which are just a short boat ride away. There are also the botanical Gardens of Villa Taranto and lots of nice walks straight from your hotel. When you’re not out seeing the sights, explore the old town where bars and restaurants spill out onto cobbled squares, and enjoy leisurely strolls along the lakefront promenade.</p>
<p><strong>Day 11: Lake Maggiore</strong></p>
<p>Enjoy a final day to relax in the sunshine and enjoy the beautiful lake. </p>
<p><strong>Day 12: Stresa to UK </strong></p>
<p>Transfer to the airport for your flight home.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/maggiore-and-como-medley">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h3><a name="Your holiday includes"></a></h3>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Your holiday includes</h3>
<ul>
<li>7, 11 or 14 nights accommodation</li>
<li>A choice of accommodation in one of our Lake Como resorts (Bellagio, Menaggio or Lenno)</li>
<li>A choice of accommodation in Stresa</li>
<li>Return flights to Milan from the UK</li>
<li>Airport transfers</li>
<li>Direct transfers between resorts</li>
</ul>
<p><span></span><strong>Your holiday excludes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Any optional extra excursions</li>
<li>Tourist Tax</li>
<li>Any extras, drinks, gratuities and personal expenses </li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/maggiore-and-como-medley">[Back to top]</a></p>
<h3><a name="Hotels"></a></h3>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Hotels</h3>
<p>Choose from a selection of our hotels in <a data-udi="umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/44b05c95e1264c56b51016621b99f80b}" title="Stresa">Stresa</a> and a selection of our hotels in one of our Lake Como resorts (Bellagio, Menaggio or Lenno). Give us a call to discuss your options.</p>
<h3><a name="Departure dates"></a></h3>
<h3 style="color: #00533a;">Departure dates<a></a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Wednesday and Saturday departures from early May to early September</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/maggiore-and-como-medley">[Back to top]</a></p>]]></description>
